docs {
  ## List Role
  แสดงรายการบทบาททั้งหมดพร้อมการแบ่งหน้าและค้นหา

  Lists all named role bundles defined in the ERP platform, such as Admin, Purchaser, HOD, or General Manager. These roles group permissions together to simplify user access management across hotel properties.

  ### Query Parameters
  | Name | Type | Required | Default | Description |
  |------|------|----------|---------|-------------|
  | `version` | string | No | latest | API version |

  ### Headers
  | Name | Required | Description |
  |------|----------|-------------|
  | `Authorization` | Yes | `Bearer {{access_token}}` |
  | `x-app-id` | Yes | `{{x_app_id}}` |

  ### Permissions
  Platform admin only — managed at Keycloak realm role level

  ### Sample Response
  ```json
  {
    "data": [
      {
        "id": "019638a6-2a00-7c4f-8e46-9b7a52c80c4d",
        "name": "Purchaser",
        "code": "PURCHASER",
        "description": "Role for procurement officers",
        "is_active": true
      }
    ],
    "paginate": {
      "page": 1,
      "perpage": 10,
      "pages": 1,
      "total": 4,
      "prev": null,
      "next": null
    },
    "status": 200,
    "success": true,
    "message": "Success",
    "timestamp": "2026-04-29T08:30:00.000Z"
  }
  ```

  ### Error Responses
  | Status | When |
  |--------|------|
  | 401 | Missing or invalid bearer token |
}
